Apache/conf/httpd.conf
---------

DocumentRoot "X:/dev/webApp/"

<Directory "X:/dev/webApp/">

(CATALINA_BASE)/webapps/, there is a directory called ROOT (the capitals are important, even under Windows). 
That is the residence of the current Tomcat default application, the one that is called right now when a user calls up  
http://myhost.company.com[:port]
